item.description: Check out the Open Mic at the TCAN, Natick Center for the Arts. The Open mic sign-ups will begin at 7:30 pm and the show starts at 8pm. The cost is $5. The feature performer is Bethel Steele. Come and play!
item.how_to_find_us: Call me at 857.492.6020 or look around for me with my small tan guitar case.
